in.
Shirley
asked
her
why
she
came
so
late.
"Because
I
have
been
making
my
dress,"
said
she.
"These
fine
sunny
days
began
to
make
me
ashamed
of
my
winter
merino,
so
I
have
furbished
up
a
lighter
